---
import MathPageLayout from '../../../layouts/MathPageLayout.astro';
---

<MathPageLayout title="유형 01. [중] 실력 향상" chapter="Level: Mid">
  <div slot="cues">
<p style="margin: 0; font-weight: bold; color: #1a1a1a;">🔵 응용 포인트</p>
				<ul style="margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 18px; font-size: 11pt; line-height: 1.6; color: #444;">
					<li>복잡한 다항식 전개</li>
					<li>분수 항 내의 연산 주의</li>
				</ul>
  </div>

  <section>
<div class="type-section">
					<p style="margin-bottom: 20px;">다항식의 전개와 차수를 고려하여 정확한 값을 도출하는 연습입니다.</p>
					
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q1.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type01-mid/q1" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{(2x+1)(3x-5)}{x^2 + 10} $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q2 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q2.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type01-mid/q2" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{(x+2)^2}{3x^2 - x} $" }
						</div>
					</div>

					<!-- Q3 -->
					<div class="question-card">
						<div class="question-header">
							<p style="margin: 0;"><b>Q3.</b> 다음 극한값을 구하시오.</p>
							<a href="/wiki/chapter01/solutions/type01-mid/q3" class="sol-button">풀이 💡</a>
						</div>
						<div class="formula-box" style="text-align: center;">
							{ "$ \\displaystyle \\lim_{x \\to \\infty} \\frac{2x^2 + 5x}{(x-1)(x+3)} $" }
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top: 40px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 15px;">
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/types/type01/" class="problem-link" style="margin: 0;">← 핵심 문제로 이동</a>
					<a href="/wiki/chapter01/problems-inf/" class="problem-link" style="margin: 0; background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.05); color: #666;">목록으로 돌아가기</a>
				</div>
  </section>
</MathPageLayout>

<style>
.sol-button {
				display: inline-block;
				padding: 4px 12px;
				background: #eef2f8;
				color: #1a73e8;
				border-radius: 8px;
				text-decoration: none;
				font-size: 0.9rem;
				font-weight: bold;
				margin-left: 10px;
				border: 1.5px solid #d0e0f0;
				transition: all 0.2s ease;
			}
			.sol-button:hover {
				background: #1a73e8;
				color: white;
				transform: translateY(-1px);
				box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(26, 115, 232, 0.2);
			}
</style>
